    "---\n",
    "## 3 — Data Pre-processing and Preparation\n",
    "\n",
    "Before training, raw data must be cleaned and transformed. The following table summarizes the pre-processing steps applied:\n",
    "\n",
    "| Problem in Dataset | Pre-processing Technique | Justification |\n",
    "|--------------------|--------------------------|---------------|\n",
    "| Categorical target (`B`/`M`) | Label Encoding → `0`/`1` | ML models require numerical labels |\n",
    "| Different feature scales | StandardScaler (Z-score) | SVM, KNN, and ANN are scale-sensitive |\n",
    "| Class imbalance (357 B vs 212 M) | `class_weight='balanced'` in models | Avoids bias toward majority class |\n",
    "| Missing values | Check and handle | Incomplete data corrupts training |\n",
    "| Data leakage risk | Scale **after** split | Prevents test information leaking into training |"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 38,
   "id": "606cc17e",
   "metadata": {},
